snippet.title: Fate/EXTELLA: The Umbral Star - Official Game Trailer - Nintendo E3 2017
snippet.description:
The famous Fate series now strikes a path to a new stage with the newest title, Fate/EXTELLA: The Umbral Star, coming to Nintendo Switch on July 25, 2017.
